{"tid":148371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捐屎有錢收港人搶住捐 1個月接1萬份申請","createTime":"2017-03-08T14:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T15:18:57.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a47e6c5fbb6f8f1be1560d69ebee115aec926fe9","tid":148371,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"捐屎有錢賺。亞洲益菌中心在香港招募「捐屎者」，收集最健康的1％香港人的糞便益菌樣本，每捐一次屎，可獲贈交通津貼200元，引起港人熱議。中心指在短短1個月內，破紀錄已接獲近1萬份申請，認為是證明香港是一個社會參與公共衛生的理想都市。<br />\n<br />\n中心表示，將來會在亞洲另外3個地區也設立糞菌銀行，收集並提供健康的人類腸道菌群。中心與本港醫生和醫院合作，純化的菌群會用於醫治特定的病人。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲益菌中心仍正繼續招募糞便捐贈者，只要介乎18至50歲，BMI指數30以下，有健康腸胃及過去3個月沒服藥或抗生素，可到網站（ <a href=\"http://www.asiabiobank.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiabiobank.com&d=xzf4O3tGv54ZmzQe4QccrHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=91e91c45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.asiabiobank.com</a> ）登記。<br />\n<br />\n邊個爭住去捐屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bbdf157e9d311749f7045525c0cad29e484642","tid":148371,"uid":84585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9db1f1f59b88c1a2cc8a2f31f6081083e06119db","tid":148371,"uid":9531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"香港幾時有捐精<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af61d5e06ce21a0291e1a284fafbcf7c9a8a19c2","tid":148371,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:57:12.000Z","msg":"證明香港是一個社會參與公共衛生的理想都市<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db8adbb9f596025b2d69e3bee2b0ee819438093","tid":148371,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:01:14.000Z","msg":"有錢收日日捐又點話"},{"pid":"53b3f433f4ffd7f147875b3c4d42cef774e74950","tid":148371,"uid":18944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明香港是一個社會參與公共衛生的理想都市<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑死人"},{"pid":"db730578edd110981d70a7c31e5452b3eef0bf14","tid":148371,"uid":38738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"日日都要屙屎<br />\n有屎屙有錢收有女溝<br />\n何樂而不為？<br />\n<br />\n利申冇申請"}]}